= Shopping Trike

A shopping cart for RadiantCMS.

= Notice
Real documentation is forthcoming.

= An example store
The following page parts create a simple store with minimal layout.

body:
  Buy our stuff.<br/><br/>

  <r:shopping:product:each>
    <r:shopping:product:link>
      <r:shopping:product:code/>
    </r:shopping:product:link>
    <r:shopping:product:addtocart/>
    <br/>
  </r:shopping:product:each>

  <r:content part="cart" />
    
product:
  <r:shopping:product:code/>:<r:shopping:product:description/> will only cost you <r:shopping:product:price/> if you buy it right now!
  <br/><br/>

  Want to buy this product? <r:shopping:product:addtocart/>

  <r:content part="cart"/>

cart:
  <r:shopping:cart:form>
  Your cart contains:<br/>
    <r:shopping:cart:item:each>
      An item <r:shopping:cart:item:code/> is <r:shopping:cart:item:unitcost />/unit &times; <r:shopping:cart:item:quantity/> = <r:shopping:cart:item:subtotal />, change quantity to:<r:shopping:cart:item:update/> or <r:shopping:cart:item:remove/>
      <hr/>
    </r:shopping:cart:item:each>
    Total cost: <r:shopping:cart:total /><br/>
    <r:shopping:cart:empty />
    <r:shopping:cart:update /><br />
    <r:shopping:cart:checkout /><br/>
  </r:shopping:cart:form>
  
checkout:
  Review your cart contents:<br/>
  <r:content part="cart"/>

  <hr/>

  <r:shopping:checkout:process processor_url="http://example.com/cart_capture.html" next_url="http://example.com/payment_step1.html"/>

For the AJAXified shopping cart to work correctly, the layout used for Store pages
must include the prototype.js library. To include the library simply insert
  <script src="/javascripts/prototype.js" language="JavaScript" type="text/javascript"></script>
into you layouts head.
